    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    App
    Main application class for the SwiftFox JavaFX-based process scheduling simulator.
    FCFS
    First-Come, First-Served (FCFS) scheduling algorithm implementation.
    GanttChart
    Represents the Gantt chart used to visualize the execution timeline of processes in the SwiftFox CPU Scheduler Simulator.
    GanttEntry
    Represents a single entry in the Gantt chart for the CPU scheduling simulation.
    PrimaryController
    Controller class for the main screen of the SwiftFox CPU Scheduler Simulator.
    Priority
    Priority-based scheduling algorithm implementation.
    Process
    Represents a process in the CPU scheduling simulation.
    Process.State
    Represents the possible states of a process during the simulation lifecycle.
    ProcessMetrics
    A record representing performance metrics of a process, including turnaround time and waiting time.
    Results
    A utility class that analyzes a GanttChart to compute metrics such as waiting time and turnaround time for each Process.
    RR
    Round Robin (RR) scheduling algorithm implementation.
    Scheduler
    Abstract base class representing a CPU scheduler.
    Simulator
    Simulates the execution of scheduling algorithms over a list of Processes.
    SJF
    Shortest Job First (SJF) scheduling algorithm.
    Test
    Runs a test simulation using the Priority scheduling algorithm (non-preemptive).
    UI_controller
    Controller class for the main simulation interface of the SwiftFox CPU Scheduler Simulator.
